@startuml 09-reports
skinparam backgroundColor #F1F5F9
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title <font size=18 color=#0F172A><b>Reports</b></font>\n<font color=#64748B>Route: /projects/:id/reports</font>

salt
{+
  {
    <font color=#1E40AF><b>Project Cost Control</b></font> | . | . | ^Citizens Medical Center (23CON0002)^ | <font color=#64748B><&person></font>
  }
  ---
  {
    [Dashboard] | [Budget] | [Employees] | [Time Entry] | [Actuals] | [Projections] | [<b>Reports</b>]
  }
  ---
  {
    <font size=14 color=#0F172A><b>Reports</b></font>
  }
  .
  {+
    <font color=#1E40AF><b><&bar-chart> Executive Summary</b></font>
    <font color=#64748B>One-page project health overview with key metrics and GP analysis</font>
    . | . | . | [  Preview  ] | [  Export PDF  ]
  }
  .
  {+
    <font color=#1E40AF><b><&spreadsheet> Budget vs Actual Report</b></font>
    <font color=#64748B>Detailed variance analysis by cost code with budget tracking</font>
    . | . | . | [  Preview  ] | [  Export PDF  ]
  }
  .
  {+
    <font color=#1E40AF><b><&graph> Monthly Trend Report</b></font>
    <font color=#64748B>Cost and hours trends over time with visual charts</font>
    . | . | . | [  Preview  ] | [  Export PDF  ]
  }
  .
  {+
    <font color=#1E40AF><b><&layers> Projection History</b></font>
    <font color=#64748B>Compare projection snapshots and GP% trends over time</font>
    . | . | . | [  Preview  ] | [  Export PDF  ]
  }
}

note right
  <b>Features</b>
  ----
  4 report types available
  Preview on screen
  Export as PDF (client-side)
  Print-optimized layout
  ----
  Data sources:
  - Budget entries
  - Monthly actuals
  - Projection snapshots
  ----
  All roles can view/export
end note

@enduml
